    "description": "Core Concept Technologies Inc. engages in the provision of digital transformation support in Japan. The company offers Orizuru, a digital development base for the manufacturing, construction, and logistics industries; Orizuru MES for manufacturing execution; Orizuru 3D for estimating, design, and procurement; and cloud solutions, inclusing sales support, frontend and backend core business management, workflow and expense management, AI agent, document and report management, and data analysis. It also provides meviy, an AI platform for procuring machine parts; support for staffing of IT personnel for business companies, system integrators, and consulting firms; and Ohgi, a network of IT staffing business partners. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Toshima, Japan."
